3254static int check_snmp_from(const qv_t(lstr) *words)
3255{
3256 if (words->len <= 1) {
3257 return -1;
3258 }
3259 tab_for_each_entry(word, words) {
3260 if (!word.len) {
3261 return -1;
3262 }
3263 }
3264 return 0;
3265}
3266
3267static int parse_struct_snmp_from(iopc_parser_t *pp, iopc_pkg_t **pkg,
3268 iopc_path_t **path, char **name)
3269{
3270 t_scope;
3271 pstream_t ps = ps_initstr(TK_N(pp, 0)->b.data);
3272 ctype_desc_t sep;
3273 iopc_path_t *path_new;
3274 qv_t(lstr) words;
3275
3276 ctype_desc_build(&sep, ".");
3277
3278 if (!ps_has_char_in_ctype(&ps, &sep)) {
3279 return parse_struct_type(pp, pkg, path, name);
3280 }
3281
3282 path_new = iopc_path_new();
3283 path_new->loc = TK_N(pp, 0)->loc;
3284 t_qv_init(&words, 2);
3285
3286 /* Split the token */
3287 ps_split(ps, &sep, 0, &words);
3288
3289 if (check_snmp_from(&words) < 0) {
3290 error_loc("invalid snmpParamsFrom `%*pM`", path_new->loc,
3291 PS_FMT_ARG(&ps));
3292 goto error;
3293 }
3294
3295 /* Get the path */
3296 for (int i = 0; i < words.len - 1; i++) {
3297 qv_append(&path_new->bits, lstr_dup(words.tab[i]).v);
3298 }
3299 if (pkg) {
3300 *pkg = check_path_exists(pp, path_new);
3301 if (!(*pkg)) {
3302 goto error;
3303 }
3304 }
3305
3306 *path = path_new;
3307 *name = lstr_dup(words.tab[words.len - 1]).v;
3308
3309 DROP(pp, 1);
3310 return 0;
3311
3312 error:
3313 iopc_path_delete(&path_new);
3314 return -1;
3315}
3316
3317static int parse_snmp_attr_arg(iopc_parser_t *pp, iopc_attr_t *attr,
3318 iopc_arg_desc_t *desc)
3319{
3320 iopc_arg_t arg;
3321
3322 iopc_arg_init(&arg);
3323 arg.desc = desc;
3324 arg.loc = TK_N(pp, 0)->loc;
3325 arg.v.s = lstr_dup(LSTR(TK_N(pp, 0)->b.data));
3326 e_trace(1, "%s=(id)%s", desc->name.s, arg.v.s.s);
3327
3328 WANT(pp, 0, ITOK_IDENT);
3329 arg.type = ITOK_IDENT;
3330 qv_append(&attr->args, arg);
3331
3332 do {
3333 iopc_extends_t *xt = iopc_extends_new();
3334
3335 qv_append(&attr->snmp_params_from, xt);
3336 xt->loc = TK_N(pp, 0)->loc;
3337 RETHROW(parse_struct_snmp_from(pp, &xt->pkg, &xt->path, &xt->name));
3338 iopc_loc_merge(&xt->loc, TK_N(pp, 0)->loc);
3339 } while (SKIP_N(pp, ','));
3340
3341 return 0;
3342}
3343
3344static int parse_attr_arg(iopc_parser_t *pp, iopc_attr_t *attr,
3345 iopc_arg_desc_t *desc)
3346{
3347 iopc_arg_t arg;
3348
3349 if (!desc) {
3350 /* expect named argument: arg=val */
3351 lstr_t str;
3352 bool found = false;
3353
3354 WANT(pp, 0, ITOK_IDENT);
3355 str = LSTR(TK_N(pp, 0)->b.data);
3356
3357 tab_for_each_ptr(d, &attr->desc->args) {
3358 if (lstr_equal(str, d->name)) {
3359 desc = d;
3360 found = true;
3361 break;
3362 }
3363 }
3364 if (!found) {
3365 throw_loc("incorrect argument name", TK_N(pp, 0)->loc);
3366 }
3367 DROP(pp, 1);
3368 EAT(pp, '=');
3369 }
3370
3371 if (!IOPC_ATTR_REPEATED_MONO_ARG(attr->desc)) {
3372 tab_for_each_ptr(a, &attr->args) {
3373 if (a->desc == desc) {
3374 throw_loc("duplicated argument", TK_N(pp, 0)->loc);
3375 }
3376 }
3377 }
3378
3379 iopc_arg_init(&arg);
3380 arg.desc = desc;
3381 arg.loc = TK_N(pp, 0)->loc;
3382
3383 if (desc->type == ITOK_DOUBLE) {
3384 if (CHECK_N(pp, 0, desc->type)) {
3385 arg.type = desc->type;
3386 } else {
3387 WANT(pp, 0, ITOK_INTEGER);
3388 arg.type = ITOK_INTEGER;
3389 }
3390 } else {
3391 WANT(pp, 0, desc->type);
3392 arg.type = desc->type;
3393 }
3394
3395 switch (arg.type) {
3396 case ITOK_STRING:
3397 arg.v.s = lstr_dup(LSTR(TK_N(pp, 0)->b.data));
3398 e_trace(1, "%s=(str)%s", desc->name.s, arg.v.s.s);
3399 DROP(pp, 1);
3400 break;
3401
3402 case ITOK_DOUBLE:
3403 arg.v.d = TK_N(pp,0)->d;
3404 e_trace(1, "%s=(double)%f", desc->name.s, arg.v.d);
3405 DROP(pp, 1);
3406 break;
3407
3408 case ITOK_IDENT:
3409 arg.v.s = lstr_dup(LSTR(TK_N(pp, 0)->b.data));
3410 e_trace(1, "%s=(id)%s", desc->name.s, arg.v.s.s);
3411 DROP(pp, 1);
3412 break;
3413
3414 case ITOK_INTEGER:
3415 case ITOK_BOOL:
3416 RETHROW(parse_constant_integer(pp, ')', (uint64_t *)&arg.v.i64,
3417 NULL));
3418 e_trace(1, "%s=(i64)%jd", desc->name.s, arg.v.i64);
3419 break;
3420
3421 default:
3422 throw_error("incorrect type for argument %*pM",
3423 LSTR_FMT_ARG(desc->name));
3424 }
3425
3426 qv_append(&attr->args, arg);
3427 return 0;
3428}
3429
3430static int parse_attr_args(iopc_parser_t *pp, iopc_attr_t *attr, lstr_t *out)
3431{
3432 bool explicit = false;
3433 iopc_arg_desc_t *desc = NULL;
3434 int i = 0;
3435
3436 *out = LSTR_NULL_V;
3437
3438 iopc_lexer_push_state_attr(pp->ld);
3439
3440 if (CHECK_N(pp, 1, '=')) {
3441 explicit = true;
3442 }
3443
3444 while (!CHECK_NOEOF_N(pp, 0, ')')) {
3445 if (!explicit) {
3446 if (IOPC_ATTR_REPEATED_MONO_ARG(attr->desc)) {
3447 desc = &attr->desc->args.tab[0];
3448 } else
3449 if (i >= attr->desc->args.len) {
3450 throw_loc("too many arguments", attr->loc);
3451 } else {
3452 desc = &attr->desc->args.tab[i++];
3453 }
3454 }
3455
3456 if (attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_GENERIC) {
3457 if (explicit) {
3458 throw_loc("invalid name for generic attribute: "
3459 "`=` is forbidden", attr->loc);
3460 }
3461 RETHROW(parse_gen_attr_arg(pp, attr, desc, out));
3462 WANT(pp, 0, ')');
3463 break;
3464 } else
3465 if (attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_SNMP_PARAMS_FROM) {
3466 RETHROW(parse_snmp_attr_arg(pp, attr, desc));
3467 WANT(pp, 0, ')');
3468 break;
3469 } else {
3470 RETHROW(parse_attr_arg(pp, attr, desc));
3471 if (CHECK_N(pp, 0, ')')) {
3472 break;
3473 }
3474 EAT(pp, ',');
3475 }
3476 }
3477 iopc_lexer_pop_state(pp->ld);
3478 DROP(pp, 1);
3479
3480 if (IOPC_ATTR_REPEATED_MONO_ARG(attr->desc) && !attr->args.len) {
3481 throw_loc("attribute %*pM expects at least one argument", attr->loc,
3482 LSTR_FMT_ARG(attr->desc->name));
3483 }
3484 if (!IOPC_ATTR_REPEATED_MONO_ARG(attr->desc)
3485 && attr->args.len != attr->desc->args.len)
3486 {
3487 throw_loc("attribute %*pM expects %d arguments, got %d", attr->loc,
3488 LSTR_FMT_ARG(attr->desc->name), attr->desc->args.len,
3489 attr->args.len);
3490 }
3491
3492 if (attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_MIN_OCCURS
3493 || attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_MAX_OCCURS
3494 || attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_MIN_LENGTH
3495 || attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_MAX_LENGTH
3496 || attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_LENGTH)
3497 {
3498 if (!attr->args.tab[0].v.i64) {
3499 throw_loc("zero value invalid for attribute %*pM", attr->loc,
3500 LSTR_FMT_ARG(attr->desc->name));
3501 }
3502 }
3503
3504 if (attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_CTYPE) {
3505 tab_for_each_ptr(arg, &attr->args) {
3506 lstr_t ctype = arg->v.s;
3507
3508 if (!lstr_endswith(ctype, LSTR("__t"))) {
3509 throw_loc("invalid ctype `%*pM`: missing __t suffix",
3510 attr->loc, LSTR_FMT_ARG(ctype));
3511 }
3512 }
3513 }
3514
3515 return 0;
3516}
3517
3518static iopc_attr_t *parse_attr(iopc_parser_t *pp)
3519{
3520 iopc_attr_t *attr;
3521 lstr_t name;
3522 int pos;
3523
3524 WANT_P(pp, 0, ITOK_ATTR);
3525
3526 attr = iopc_attr_new();
3527 attr->loc = TK(pp, 0, goto error)->loc;
3528
3529 name = LSTR(ident(TK(pp, 0, goto error)));
3530 pos = qm_find(attr_desc, &_G.attrs, &name);
3531 if (pos < 0) {
3532 error_loc("incorrect attribute name", attr->loc);
3533 goto error;
3534 }
3535 attr->desc = &_G.attrs.values[pos];
3536 DROP(pp, 1);
3537
3538 /* Generic attributes */
3539 if (attr->desc->id == IOPC_ATTR_GENERIC) {
3540 assert (attr->desc->args.len == 1);
3541
3542 if (parse_attr_args(pp, attr, &attr->real_name) < 0
3543 || !attr->real_name.s)
3544 {
3545 goto error;
3546 }
3547 return attr;
3548 }
3549
3550 if (!SKIP(pp, '(', goto error)) {
3551 if (attr->desc->args.len > 0) {
3552 error_loc("attribute arguments missing", attr->loc);
3553 goto error;
3554 }
3555 return attr;
3556 }
3557 if (attr->desc->args.len == 0) {
3558 error_loc("attribute should not have arguments", attr->loc);
3559 goto error;
3560 }
3561
3562 if (parse_attr_args(pp, attr, &name) < 0) {
3563 lstr_wipe(&name);
3564 goto error;
3565 }
3566 return attr;
3567
3568 error:
3569 iopc_attr_delete(&attr);
3570 return NULL;
3571}

3573
3574static int check_pkg_path(iopc_parser_t *pp, iopc_path_t *path,
3575 const char *base)
3576{
3577 int fd = iopc_lexer_fd(pp->ld);
3578 struct stat st1, st2;
3579 char buf[PATH_MAX];
3580
3581 snprintf(buf, sizeof(buf), "%s/%s", base, iopc_path_slash(path));
3582 path_simplify(buf);
3583 if (stat(get_full_path(buf), &st1)) {
3584 throw_loc("incorrect package name", path->loc);
3585 }
3586 if (fstat(fd, &st2)) {
3587 throw_loc("fstat error on fd %d", path->loc, fd);
3588 }
3589 if (st1.st_dev != st2.st_dev || st1.st_ino != st2.st_ino) {
3590 throw_loc("incorrect package name", path->loc);
3591 }
3592
3593 return 0;
3594}
3595
3596static int add_iface(iopc_pkg_t *pkg, iopc_iface_t *iface,
3597 qm_t(iopc_struct) *mod_inter, const char *obj)
3598{
3599 qv_append(&pkg->ifaces, iface);
3600 if (qm_add(iopc_struct, mod_inter, iface->name, (iopc_struct_t *)iface)) {
3601 throw_loc("%s named `%s` already exists", iface->loc,
3602 obj, iface->name);
3603 }
3604 return 0;
3605}
3606
3607/* Force struct, enum and union to have distinguished name (things qm)*/
3608/* Force module and interface to have distinguished name (mod_inter qm)*/
3609static iopc_pkg_t *parse_package(iopc_parser_t *pp, char *file,
3610 iopc_file_t type, bool is_main_pkg)
3611{
3612 iopc_pkg_t *pkg = iopc_pkg_new();
3613 qm_t(iopc_struct) things = QM_INIT_CACHED(struct, things);
3614 qm_t(iopc_struct) mod_inter = QM_INIT_CACHED(struct, mod_inter);
3615 qv_t(iopc_attr) attrs;
3616 qv_t(dox_chunk) chunks;
3617
3618 qv_inita(&attrs, 16);
3619 qv_inita(&chunks, 16);
3620
3621 pkg->file = file;
3622
3623 if (read_dox_front(pp, &chunks) < 0
3624 || !(pkg->name = parse_pkg_stmt(pp))
3625 || read_dox_back(pp, &chunks, 0) < 0
3626 || build_dox_check_all(&chunks, pkg) < 0)
3627 {
3628 goto error;
3629 }
3630
3631 if (type != IOPC_FILE_STDIN) {
3632 char base[PATH_MAX];
3633
3634 path_dirname(base, sizeof(base), file);
3635 for (int i = 0; i < pkg->name->bits.len - 1; i++) {
3636 path_join(base, sizeof(base), "..");
3637 }
3638 path_simplify(base);
3639 if (type == IOPC_FILE_FD) {
3640 if (check_pkg_path(pp, pkg->name, base) < 0) {
3641 goto error;
3642 }
3643 }
3644 pp->base = pkg->base = p_strdup(base);
3645 qm_add(iopc_pkg, &_G.pkgs, iopc_path_dot(pkg->name), pkg);
3646 if (is_main_pkg && pp->includes) {
3647 qv_push(pp->includes, pkg->base);
3648 }
3649 }
3650
3651 while (!CHECK(pp, 0, ITOK_EOF, goto error)) {
3652 const char *id;
3653 bool is_abstract = false;
3654 bool is_local = false;
3655
3656 if (check_dox_and_attrs(pp, &chunks, &attrs) < 0) {
3657 goto error;
3658 }
3659 if (!attrs.len && CHECK(pp, 0, ITOK_EOF, goto error)) {
3660 break;
3661 }
3662
3663 if (!CHECK(pp, 0, ITOK_IDENT, goto error)) {
3664 error_loc("expected identifier", TK(pp, 0, goto error)->loc);
3665 goto error;
3666 }
3667
3668#define SET_ATTRS_AND_COMMENTS(_o, _t) \
3669 do { \
3670 tab_enumerate(pos, _attr, &attrs) { \
3671 if (check_attr_type_decl(_attr, _t) < 0) { \
3672 qv_skip(&attrs, pos); \
3673 goto error; \
3674 } \
3675 qv_append(&_o->attrs, _attr); \
3676 } \
3677 qv_clear(&attrs); \
3678 if (read_dox_back(pp, &chunks, 0) < 0 \
3679 || build_dox(&chunks, _o, _t) < 0) \
3680 { \
3681 goto error; \
3682 } \
3683 } while (0)
3684
3685 for (int i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
3686 if (SKIP_KW(pp, "abstract", goto error)) {
3687 if (is_abstract) {
3688 error_loc("repetition of `abstract` keyword",
3689 TK(pp, 0, goto error)->loc);
3690 goto error;
3691 }
3692 is_abstract = true;
3693 } else
3694 if (SKIP_KW(pp, "local", goto error)) {
3695 if (is_local) {
3696 error_loc("repetition of `local` keyword",
3697 TK(pp, 0, goto error)->loc);
3698 goto error;
3699 }
3700 is_local = true;
3701 } else {
3702 break;
3703 }
3704 }
3705
3706 id = ident(TK(pp, 0, goto error));
3707
3708#define PARSE_STRUCT(_id, _type, _attr) \
3709 if (strequal(id, _id)) { \
3710 iopc_struct_t *st = iopc_struct_new(); \
3711 \
3712 qv_append(&pkg->structs, st); \
3713 SKIP_KW(pp, _id, goto error); \
3714 if (parse_struct_class_union_snmp_stmt(pp, _type, is_abstract, \
3715 is_local, \
3716 is_main_pkg, st) < 0) \
3717 { \
3718 goto error; \
3719 } \
3720 SET_ATTRS_AND_COMMENTS(st, _attr); \
3721 if (iopc_is_snmp_tbl(_type)) { \
3722 if (check_snmp_brief(st->comments, st->loc, st->name, \
3723 _id) < 0) \
3724 { \
3725 goto error; \
3726 } \
3727 } \
3728 \
3729 if (qm_add(iopc_struct, &things, st->name, st)) { \
3730 error_loc("something named `%s` already exists", \
3731 st->loc, st->name); \
3732 goto error; \
3733 } \
3734 continue; \
3735 }
3736
3737 PARSE_STRUCT("struct", STRUCT_TYPE_STRUCT, IOPC_ATTR_T_STRUCT);
3738 PARSE_STRUCT("class", STRUCT_TYPE_CLASS,
3739 IOPC_ATTR_T_STRUCT | IOPC_ATTR_T_CLASS);
3740 PARSE_STRUCT("snmpObj", STRUCT_TYPE_SNMP_OBJ, IOPC_ATTR_T_SNMP_OBJ);
3741 PARSE_STRUCT("snmpTbl", STRUCT_TYPE_SNMP_TBL, IOPC_ATTR_T_SNMP_TBL);
3742 PARSE_STRUCT("union", STRUCT_TYPE_UNION, IOPC_ATTR_T_UNION);
3743#undef PARSE_STRUCT
3744
3745
3746 if (strequal(id, "enum")) {
3747 iopc_enum_t *en = iopc_enum_new();
3748
3749 qv_append(&pkg->enums, en);
3750 if (parse_enum_stmt(pp, &attrs, en) < 0) {
3751 goto error;
3752 }
3753 SET_ATTRS_AND_COMMENTS(en, IOPC_ATTR_T_ENUM);
3754
3755 if (qm_add(iopc_struct, &things, en->name, (iopc_struct_t *)en)) {
3756 error_loc("something named `%s` already exists",
3757 en->loc, en->name);
3758 goto error;
3759 }
3760 continue;
3761 }
3762
3763 if (strequal(id, "interface")) {
3764 iopc_iface_t *iface;
3765 const char *obj = "interface";
3766
3767 if (!(iface = parse_iface_stmt(pp, IFACE_TYPE_IFACE, obj,
3768 is_main_pkg)))
3769 {
3770 goto error;
3771 }
3772 if (add_iface(pkg, iface, &mod_inter, obj) < 0) {
3773 goto error;
3774 }
3775 SET_ATTRS_AND_COMMENTS(iface, IOPC_ATTR_T_IFACE);
3776 continue;
3777 }
3778
3779 if (strequal(id, "snmpIface")) {
3780 iopc_iface_t *iface;
3781 const char *obj = "snmpIface";
3782
3783 if (!(iface = parse_iface_stmt(pp, IFACE_TYPE_SNMP_IFACE, obj,
3784 is_main_pkg)))
3785 {
3786 goto error;
3787 }
3788 if (add_iface(pkg, iface, &mod_inter, obj) < 0) {
3789 goto error;
3790 }
3791 SET_ATTRS_AND_COMMENTS(iface, IOPC_ATTR_T_SNMP_IFACE);
3792 continue;
3793 }
3794
3795 if (strequal(id, "module")) {
3796 iopc_struct_t *mod = parse_module_stmt(pp);
3797
3798 if (!mod) {
3799 goto error;
3800 }
3801 qv_append(&pkg->modules, mod);
3802 SET_ATTRS_AND_COMMENTS(mod, IOPC_ATTR_T_MOD);
3803
3804 if (qm_add(iopc_struct, &mod_inter, mod->name,
3805 (iopc_struct_t *)mod))
3806 {
3807 error_loc("something named `%s` already exists",
3808 mod->loc, mod->name);
3809 goto error;
3810 }
3811 continue;
3812 }
3813
3814 if (strequal(id, "typedef")) {
3815 iopc_field_t *tdef = iopc_field_new();
3816
3817 qv_append(&pkg->typedefs, tdef);
3818
3819 if (parse_typedef_stmt(pp, tdef) < 0) {
3820 goto error;
3821 }
3822
3823 tab_enumerate(pos, attr, &attrs) {
3824 if (check_attr_type_field(attr, tdef, true) < 0) {
3825 qv_skip(&attrs, pos);
3826 goto error;
3827 }
3828 qv_append(&tdef->attrs, attr);
3829 }
3830 qv_clear(&attrs);
3831 if (qm_add(iopc_struct, &things, tdef->name,
3832 (iopc_struct_t *)tdef))
3833 {
3834 error_loc("something named `%s` already exists",
3835 tdef->loc, tdef->name);
3836 goto error;
3837 }
3838 continue;
3839 }
3840
3841 error_loc("unexpected keyword `%s`", TK(pp, 0, goto error)->loc, id);
3842 goto error;
3843#undef SET_ATTRS_AND_COMMENTS
3844 }
3845
3846 if (__eat(pp, ITOK_EOF) < 0) {
3847 goto error;
3848 }
3849
3850 qv_wipe(&attrs);
3851 qv_deep_wipe(&chunks, dox_chunk_wipe);
3852 qm_wipe(iopc_struct, &things);
3853 qm_wipe(iopc_struct, &mod_inter);
3854
3855 return pkg;
3856
3857 error:
3858 qv_deep_wipe(&attrs, iopc_attr_delete);
3859 qv_deep_wipe(&chunks, dox_chunk_wipe);
3860 qm_wipe(iopc_struct, &things);
3861 qm_wipe(iopc_struct, &mod_inter);
3862
3863 if (pkg->name) {
3864 qm_del_key(iopc_pkg, &_G.pkgs, iopc_path_dot(pkg->name));
3865 }
3866 iopc_pkg_delete(&pkg);
3867 return NULL;
3868}

3871
3872iopc_loc_t iopc_loc_merge2(iopc_loc_t l1, iopc_loc_t l2)
3873{
3874 assert (l1.file == l2.file);
3875 return (iopc_loc_t){
3876 .file = l1.file,
3877 .lmin = MIN(l1.lmin, l2.lmin),
3878 .cmin = MIN(l1.cmin, l2.cmin),
3879 .lmax = MAX(l1.lmax, l2.lmax),
3880 .cmax = MAX(l1.cmax, l2.cmax),
3881 };
3882}
3883
3884void iopc_loc_merge(iopc_loc_t *l1, iopc_loc_t l2)
3885{
3886 *l1 = iopc_loc_merge2(*l1, l2);
3887}
3888
3889iopc_pkg_t *iopc_parse_file(qv_t(cstr) *includes,
3890 const qm_t(iopc_env) *env,
3891 const char *file, const char *data,
3892 bool is_main_pkg)
3893{
3894 iopc_pkg_t *pkg = NULL;
3895 iopc_file_t type;
3896
3897 if (data) {
3898 type = IOPC_FILE_BUFFER;
3899 } else
3900 if (strequal(file, "-")) {
3901 type = IOPC_FILE_STDIN;
3902 } else {
3903 type = IOPC_FILE_FD;
3904 }
3905
3906 if (!pkg) {
3907 char *path;
3908 iopc_parser_t pp = {
3909 .includes = includes,
3910 .env = env,
3911 .cfolder = iop_cfolder_new(),
3912 };
3913
3914 if (type == IOPC_FILE_STDIN) {
3915 path = p_strdup("<stdin>");
3916 } else {
3917 path = p_strdup(file);
3918 }
3919
3920 if ((pp.ld = iopc_lexer_new(path, data, type))) {
3921 pkg = parse_package(&pp, path, type, is_main_pkg);
3922 } else {
3923 p_delete(&path);
3924 }
3925
3926 qv_deep_wipe(&pp.tokens, iopc_token_delete);
3927 iopc_lexer_delete(&pp.ld);
3928 iop_cfolder_delete(&pp.cfolder);
3929 }
3930
3931 if (pkg) {
3932 qm_for_each_pos(iopc_pkg, pos, &_G.pkgs) {
3933 iopc_pkg_t *p = _G.pkgs.values[pos];
3934
3935 if (p != pkg) {
3936 qh_add(iopc_pkg, &pkg->deps, p);
3937 }
3938 }
3939 }
3940
3941 return pkg;
3942}
3943
3944void iopc_parser_initialize(void)
3945{
3946 qm_init_cached(iopc_pkg, &_G.pkgs);
3947 qm_init_cached(enums, &_G.enums);
3948 qm_init_cached(enums, &_G.enums_forbidden);
3949 qm_init_cached(attr_desc, &_G.attrs);
3950 init_attributes();
3951}
3952
3953void iopc_parser_shutdown(void)
3954{
3955 qm_deep_wipe(iopc_pkg, &_G.pkgs, IGNORE, iopc_pkg_delete);
3956 qm_deep_wipe(enums, &_G.enums, p_delete, IGNORE);
3957 qm_deep_wipe(enums, &_G.enums_forbidden, p_delete, IGNORE);
3958 qm_deep_wipe(attr_desc, &_G.attrs, IGNORE, iopc_attr_desc_wipe);
3959}
